  <description><![CDATA[<p>Plan B hotel is newly built and opened in September 2020. This modern and friendly hotel is the perfect choice for anyone who is wanting a fun and memorable stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>. The situation is perfect, close to the main bus station with ski buses going directly to the different lifts in the valley and even to <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a>. Being just a five minute walk into the very centre of Chamonix and 3 minutes' to the <span>Aiguille du Midi cable car, </span>it's in a great location for all aspects of your holiday. </p>
<p>The hotels communal spaces show a real focus on fun and socialising, with a games rooms, two bowling alleys and a great central bar area which is host to many live music events and quizzes. There's a relaxation area too, with a sauna and whirlpool, great for evenings to unwind or white-out days. Here there's beauty treatments and massages if you want a real treat.</p>
<p>A modern brasserie style restaurant is where breakfast and dinner will be served. With a love of local and fresh produce. It's a great place to enjoy your dinner and a couple of drinks.</p>]]></description>
